  13:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** Sample and hold mode provides reduced power consumption, but requires a bit more setup.
  14:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  **
  15:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** For now connecting the DAC through other internal peripherals is also not supported.
  16:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  **
